1.d4
{ This is called Queen's Pawn Opening because White starts by moving the
pawn in front of their queen two steps. } 1...d6 2.c4 Nf6 3.Nc3 g6 4.Nf3 Bg7
{ Since White played the Queen's Pawn Opening [1.
d4], our system is called King's Indian Defense
[KID]. } *

